      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously pampered, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a 'new' car without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
