    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This S54-powered icon features individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline, with a recently completed Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for total mechanical peace of mind. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with bolt-action precision, and the chassis has been structurally sound-checked with professional subframe reinforcement plates installed. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, indicating original finish, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster compression. Riding on staggered Style 67 forged wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this M3 delivers the precise turn-in and high-revving linear power delivery the chassis is legendary for. Full service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
