    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its class, preserved in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior boasts its original factory finish, radiating a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional multi-stage paint correction and a lifetime ceramic coating. There are zero imperfections\u2014no stone chips, no swirl marks, and no curb rash on the pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple with no visible bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. The car has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled environment under a breathable car cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed solely by master technicians using OEM parts. A comprehensive binder containing every service receipt, the original window sticker, and two sets of keys is included. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks, smells, and performs exactly as it did on the day of delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
